Question bank
-------------

The 32 scenario questions in assets/practice-question-bank.json are
PMCOE-authored composites. They are not drawn from PMI's own practice tests
or from any other copyrighted question bank. Each scenario tests judgment
patterns aligned with PMI's published framework (e.g., Tuckman team-formation
stages, Thomas-Kilmann conflict modes, Earned Value Management formulas).
